		<span id="title-176929367" class="story-title"> <a   href="//science.slashdot.org/story/25/04/05/0034246/scientists-warn-indonesias-rice-megaproject-faces-failure">Scientists Warn Indonesia's Rice Megaproject Faces Failure</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.science.org/content/article/indonesia-s-planned-rice-megaproject-doomed-fail"  title="External link - https://www.science.org/content/article/indonesia-s-planned-rice-megaproject-doomed-fail" target="_blank"> (science.org) </a></span></span>

		
		
